titleStmt.title: An account of their Royal Highnesses the Duke and Dutchess of York, their arrival and reception in Scotland, the 26. of Octob. 1680 In a letter from a gentleman of their Highnesses retinue, to a friend in London.

notesStmt.note: Dated at end of text: "Edenbrough, Octob. 30. 1680.".
A satirical account of James' visit to Scotland.
Reproduction of the original in the Bodleian Library.
